          <title>Case 1. Elevations in serum aminotransferase levels during rifampin therapy.</title>
          <p>[Modified from: Corrigan D, Paton J. Hepatic enzyme abnormalities in children on triple therapy for tuberculosis. Ped Pulmonol 1999; 27: 37-42. <ext-link xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10023790">PubMed Citation</ext-link>]</p>
